Class WebSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zaproxy.zap.session.WebSession
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CookieBasedSessionManagementMethodType.CookieBasedSession, HttpAuthSessionManagementMethodType.HttpAuthSession

    public abstract class WebSession
extends Object
    A WebSession is the ZAP implementation for a session maintained during the communication with a webapp/website.
